<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #4CAF50;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #718096;
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .alert {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        padding: 10px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      code {
        display: block;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        word-break: break-word;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
      <p>Hello, <strong>{{name}}</strong>!</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to proceed:</p>
      
      <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="btn">Reset Your Password</a>

      <div class="alert">
        ‚ö†Ô∏è This link expires in 15 minutes and becomes invalid after use.
      </div>

      <p>If you're having trouble with the button, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <code>{{resetLink}}</code>

      <h3>Why did you get this email?</h3>
      <p>This request originated from IP <strong>{{ipAddress}}</strong> at <strong>{{timestamp}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>If you didn‚Äôt request this, please <a href="https://pandoragardens.com/report">report suspicious activity</a>.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        üõ°Ô∏è Pandora Gardens Team
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
